    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>SERI News June 15</title>
      <lead>Information from the State Secretariat for Education, Research and Innovation SERI</lead>
      <text link="no">&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Results of the Apprenticeship Barometer now available&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Stable situation on the apprenticeship market &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bilingual teaching in VET&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;"All the stakeholders must get involved" &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Referencing report approved&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Swiss VET and PET qualifications can now be compared all over Europe &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Professional education and training projects in the health field&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;From the cantons to the Confederation &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Federal scholarships for foreign students&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Swiss Confederation awards 235 new scholarships to researchers from 84 different countries &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2015 Bologna Ministerial Conference in Yerevan, Armenia&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Highlighting the role of education &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;European X-Ray Free-Electron Laser (European XFEL)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;New ‘super microscope' provides a glimpse of new dimensions &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Variety in innovation promotion&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;New hotspots for research and innovation &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expansion of the swissnex network&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;swissnex Singapore has fulfilled its mission - new locations being decided &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calling the International Space Station&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Baccalaureate school students in Ticino take an extraordinary excursion into space&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</text>
      <contact>medien@sbfi.admin.ch</contact>
      <link id="137845">
        <title>SERI News June 15</title>
        <uri>http://www.sbfi.admin.ch/aktuell/00399/01776/index.html?lang=en</uri>
        <position>Context</position>
      </link>
      <revisions> </revisions>
